article_id:1806,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding an Issue with the Adventurer Marty's Shared Skill Safeguard Surge,image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed that the following issue was affecting the adventurer Marty:</div><div><br></div><div>ãƒ»The skill gauge of the adventurer Marty&#39;s shared skill Safeguard Surge Lv. 2 fills more quickly than intended.</div><div><br></div><div>This issue was addressed in a data update around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1606456800"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Starting at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1606460400"></span>, we will begin sending players who unlocked the Safeguard Surge shared skill before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1606456800"></span> three flame tomes (the amount necessary to unlock it) as a goodwill gesture.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1606456800,update_time1606456981